{
  "3065800": {
    "name": "失落星船：马拉松",
    "steam_appid": 3065800,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065800/extras/f003b08f1163d02125a3fd3bc7f05e4e.poster.avif?t=1772231545\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065800/extras/f003b08f1163d02125a3fd3bc7f05e4e.webm?t=1772231545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065800/extras/f003b08f1163d02125a3fd3bc7f05e4e.mp4?t=1772231545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >潜入黑暗科幻世界——天仓五IV：这是一座废弃的殖民地，充斥着疾行者敌人、敌对UESC安全部队以及变幻莫测的环境。你可以组队或单人形式在各个区域搜寻货品。紧张刺激的探索会突然切换为快节奏的PvP战斗——枪战反应灵敏，物资有限，而周密的准备将会获得丰厚的回报。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >撤离可提升你的赛季能量，赢取成就装饰，并用掠夺来的战利品打造更强大的配装。然后带着装备重返战场，在下次疾行中搜寻更多财富。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无限可能的墓地 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065800/extras/0c1d2ddc1eb66f6834217df4145b61fa.poster.avif?t=1772231545\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065800/extras/0c1d2ddc1eb66f6834217df4145b61fa.webm?t=1772231545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065800/extras/0c1d2ddc1eb66f6834217df4145b61fa.mp4?t=1772231545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >闯入废弃的研究设施、崎岖的地形和安保前哨站，那里保存着消失远征队的残骸，等待你去发掘。天仓五危机四伏，独特敌人、动态事件和危险环境随时可能将你吞噬。每个区域的难度会逐步提升，让你为锁于天际的UESC马拉松号做好准备。   </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >强力装备。可配置。可消耗。 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065800/extras/66f103462965f068762163bc86cc1cd5.poster.avif?t=1772231545\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065800/extras/66f103462965f068762163bc86cc1cd5.webm?t=1772231545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065800/extras/66f103462965f068762163bc86cc1cd5.mp4?t=1772231545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >六种可装备的疾行者外壳提供多种玩法基础，例如毁灭者、侦察和盗贼。搜寻各种可改装的武器、身体植入物和核心系统升级，打造无数种不同的配装。每次疾行都要与队友制定策略，组建能够最大限度发挥团队优势的队伍，打造应对战斗和完成目标的方式。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >敌人无处不在 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065800/extras/9055695cb8310550cfd15d60957fff7c.poster.avif?t=1772231545\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065800/extras/9055695cb8310550cfd15d60957fff7c.webm?t=1772231545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065800/extras/9055695cb8310550cfd15d60957fff7c.mp4?t=1772231545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与两到三名队友组队面对未知挑战，或独自在单人大厅冒险。或者你可以作为鲁克，一个没有初始装备、一无所有的孤胆拾荒者，潜入进行中的团队大厅。在近距离聊天中与敌对的疾行者建立临时联盟，击败共同的敌人，但请记住，你的新盟友可能很快就会反目成仇。战斗中务必毫不留情：即使队员阵亡，唯一的幸存者也能将其重启。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在第一赛季后期，参与评值模式来检验实力，建立名声。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >影响即力量 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065800/extras/61d12a37e8ea80580ceaefcd8c2cb682.poster.avif?t=1772231545\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065800/extras/61d12a37e8ea80580ceaefcd8c2cb682.webm?t=1772231545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065800/extras/61d12a37e8ea80580ceaefcd8c2cb682.mp4?t=1772231545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与六个相互竞争的阵营联络，他们均提供丰厚奖励，以巩固其在天仓五的势力。完成阵营合约可以提升你的基础实力，解锁赛季期间的各种奖励，例如疾行者外壳升级、更强的初始配置、更大的保险库空间，以及可以用剩余战利品购买的特殊商品。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重组真相 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065800/extras/baa56d3ab1c77edb9459e98defd1de1f.poster.avif?t=1772231545\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065800/extras/baa56d3ab1c77edb9459e98defd1de1f.webm?t=1772231545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065800/extras/baa56d3ab1c77edb9459e98defd1de1f.mp4?t=1772231545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一百多年前，马拉松号远征突然失联，无人知晓发生了什么。你闯入了UESC领地，并且拥有独特优势来拼凑出这段历史的真相。你不断深入殖民地，来揭开天仓五尘封已久的秘密。     </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >死亡如影随形  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065800/extras/05a3bf7b813de51bb0acfbceca6ada19.poster.avif?t=1772231545\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065800/extras/05a3bf7b813de51bb0acfbceca6ada19.webm?t=1772231545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065800/extras/05a3bf7b813de51bb0acfbceca6ada19.mp4?t=1772231545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一旦解锁进入轨道，你要带着终极装备前往UESC马拉松号的第一层——低温档案室。破解类似突袭的安全措施，解开冰封的保险库，掠夺其中的神器。你会与装备精良、争夺同一宝藏的敌方队员狭路相逢，被迫交锋。攻破第七层保险库，挑战连UESC都畏惧的强大存在。 </p>",
